					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I found out my problem with my nametable loading wrong---apparently NESASM ignores anything after the 24th entry on any .db row. P65 does not, so it loaded my nametable fine. Has anyone else encountered this limitation of NESASM? I've looked at the available documentation for NESASM and there doesn't appear to be any mention of this limitation.</div>

